('Formoterol', 'Respiratory', 'Formoterol is a long-acting beta-2 agonist bronchodilator used for asthma and COPD. It has rapid onset and 12-hour duration.', '12-24mcg twice daily', 'Tremor, tachycardia, headache, nervousness, hypokalemia, paradoxical bronchospasm', 4.6, '$$$', 'Prescription only', 'AstraZeneca', 'Long-acting Beta-2 Agonist', 'C', 'Room temperature 20-25°C', '10-12 hours', '3-5 min', '12 hours', 'Hepatic', 'Renal', 4321, '["Beta-blockers","Diuretics","Digoxin","MAOIs","TCAs"]', '["Tachycardia","Tremor","Not for acute attacks","Asthma-related death risk"]', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584308666744-24d5c474f2ae?w=300&h=300&fit=crop', true, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
